<!DOCTYPE html>
<html ng-app="app">
<head>

    <title>CodeGen-Update</title>

    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta content="IE=edge, chrome=1" http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    
    <base href="/">

    @Styles.Render("~/content/main")

</head>
<body ng-controller="masterPageController as vm" ng-class="{'minimizedMenu': vm.minimizedMenu}" class="loading">

    <div id="wrapper">
        <!-- Navigation -->
        <nav id="topmenu" class="navbar navbar-default navbar-static-top" role="navigation" style="margin-bottom: 0">

            <div class="navbar-header">
                <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-collapse">
                    <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                </button>
                <a href="/" class="navbar-brand">
                    CODE GENERATOR
                </a>
            </div>
            <!-- /.navbar-header -->

            <ul id="topmenu" class="nav navbar-top-links navbar-right">
                <li class="dropdown" ng-if="vm.isAdmin">
                    <a href="/users"><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-down fa-fw"></i><span class="hidden-xs visible-sm-inline-block visible-md-inline-block visible-lg-inline-block inline-block">Users</span></a>
                </li>
                <li class="dropdown" ng-if="vm.isAdmin">
                    <a href="/settings"><i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-down fa-fw"></i><span class="hidden-xs visible-sm-inline-block visible-md-inline-block visible-lg-inline-block inline-block">Settings</span></a>
                </li>
                <!-- /.dropdown -->
                <li class="dropdown">
                    <a class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#" ng-cloak=""><i class="fa fa-user fa-fw"></i><span class="hidden-xs visible-sm-inline-block visible-md-inline-block visible-lg-inline-block inline-block">{{vm.identity.firstName + ' ' + vm.identity.lastName}}</span></a>
                    <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-user">
                        <li>
                            <a href="#" ng-click="vm.logout()"><i class="fa fa-sign-out fa-fw"></i>Logout</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <!-- /.dropdown-user -->
                </li>
                <!-- /.dropdown -->
            </ul>
            <!-- /.navbar-top-links -->

        </nav>

        <div id="page-wrapper">

            <ol id="breadcrumb" ncy-breadcrumb>&nbsp;</ol>

            <div class="alert alert-warning" ng-if="vm.isDemo">
                <i class="fa fa-warning"></i>&nbsp;You are not allowed to modify the demo project.
            </div>

            <div ng-cloak ui-view>
                @RenderBody()
            </div>

            <div ng-if="vm.ShowInfo">
                
                <hr />

                <div class="well">
                    <p>Hi there!</p>
                    <p>If you're interested in using this system to speed up your development, you'll need to get in touch with me to get the latest shell project that has the up-to-date controllers, stylesheets, directives, etc.</p>
                    <p>Most of it is up on <a href="https://github.com/capesean/codegenerator">Github</a>, but I don't keep it as up-to-date as I could, as I'm not sure if other people will find it useful or not. I use it almost every day, though.</p>
                    <p>So if you think this <strong>code generator</strong> might be useful to you, get in touch and I can help set you up properly. If enough people are interested, then I'll try keeping GitHub more updated!</p>
                    <p>You can get in touch via Github, or Twitter <a href="https://twitter.com/capesean">&commat;CapeSean</a></p>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

    <div id="loginForm">

        <div id="logocontainer" class="text-center">
            <h1>CODE GENERATOR</h1>
            <div id="loader"></div>
        </div>

    </div>

    @Scripts.Render("~/scripts/main")

    @RenderSection("scripts", required: false)

</body>
</html>
